==Cyrillic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''Ў''', '''ў''' (''italics: Ў, ў'')

#The 22th letter of the Belarusian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. It has a similar sound of English '''w'''. It is preceded by [[у|У]] and followed by [[ф|Ф]].

